Well, we don't know much about Joel as a person since he recorded very little about himself.

00:00:22.179 --> 00:00:26.179
So this is a great opportunity to dig into the historical context.

00:00:26.179 --> 00:00:27.179
Great idea.

00:00:27.179 --> 00:00:28.179
Where did you find it?

