That brings up another great way to find treasure.

00:02:37.180 --> 00:02:44.180
Look for Jehovah's actions, and when he took the action, Jehovah's actions reveal his character.

00:02:44.180 --> 00:02:46.180
Oh, that's a great point.

00:02:46.180 --> 00:02:51.180
So, Jehovah gives Joel this incredible message, but when?

00:02:51.180 --> 00:02:59.180
Look at the timing, about 820 BCE, more than 200 years before Jerusalem was destroyed.

00:02:59.180 --> 00:03:01.180
So, think about that.

00:03:01.180 --> 00:03:08.180
Jehovah warms his people of what is coming, and then gives them plenty of time to repent and to respond.

00:03:08.180 --> 00:03:10.180
Jehovah's so patient.

00:03:10.180 --> 00:03:15.180
Even with people who should know better, even with people who deliberately hurt him and hurt others.

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:21.180
